WEBVTT

00:15.590 --> 00:16.990
Greetings, Princess Fu.

00:17.160 --> 00:19.620
Our Princess Consort
invites you for a chat.

00:31.640 --> 00:33.960
Her Highness is waiting for you inside.

00:41.070 --> 00:42.000
Zhao Chun'er.

00:42.790 --> 00:44.450
Why did you ask me to come here?

00:48.470 --> 00:51.670
Her Majesty asked me to show you
the people you want to see—

00:51.840 --> 00:52.920
your friends.

00:59.960 --> 01:00.430
Lin Mu?

01:00.840 --> 01:01.390
Lin Mu!

01:06.720 --> 01:07.580
Your Highness!

01:07.950 --> 01:09.550
-Your Highness?
-Your Highness?

01:09.550 --> 01:10.260
Your Highness.

01:10.260 --> 01:11.520
How are your injuries?

01:12.480 --> 01:13.150
We're fine.

01:13.950 --> 01:15.350
Don't be sad, Your Highness.

01:15.350 --> 01:16.710
I'm strong.

01:18.590 --> 01:19.650
I won't die easily.

01:20.230 --> 01:20.950
Zhao Chun'er!

01:20.950 --> 01:22.350
What exactly do you want?

01:24.360 --> 01:26.770
What can a weak woman like me do?

01:27.760 --> 01:29.230
I just know you.

01:29.560 --> 01:31.090
I know you value friendship

01:31.230 --> 01:33.479
and that you must be very worried about
your friends,

01:33.479 --> 01:35.280
so I brought you here to see them.

01:35.710 --> 01:37.070
Shouldn't you thank me?

01:38.039 --> 01:38.759
After all,

01:39.400 --> 01:41.590
they were captured because of you.

01:42.590 --> 01:45.039
And they might even die because of you.

01:46.220 --> 01:47.420
This meeting today

01:48.110 --> 01:49.880
might be your last.

01:52.170 --> 01:53.009
Come at me!

01:53.150 --> 01:54.750
They've done nothing to you!

01:55.759 --> 01:56.430
Yes.

01:57.670 --> 01:58.870
I am coming at you.

01:59.150 --> 02:00.150
If it weren't for you,

02:00.150 --> 02:02.280
they wouldn't have ended up like this.

02:02.480 --> 02:04.540
For the sake of our old acquaintance,

02:04.840 --> 02:06.640
I'll show you a clear path.

02:06.640 --> 02:08.240
If you agree to marry Yan Xun,

02:08.710 --> 02:10.770
Her Majesty will agree to let them go.

02:10.840 --> 02:13.120
Otherwise, they will be branded

02:13.120 --> 02:14.520
as traitors just like you

02:14.710 --> 02:15.870
and Li Ce,

02:16.000 --> 02:17.310
and executed.

02:17.310 --> 02:18.000
Your Highness!

02:18.000 --> 02:19.120
Don't agree!

02:20.910 --> 02:21.800
So?

02:22.150 --> 02:25.010
Haven't you always prided yourself
on being great?

02:25.560 --> 02:27.280
What are you hesitating for?

02:28.079 --> 02:29.400
Do you want to stay here

02:29.400 --> 02:31.190
and keep watching them suffer!

02:31.190 --> 02:32.030
Zhao Chun'er!

02:32.050 --> 02:33.780
Living a life worse than death?

02:34.630 --> 02:35.520
I don't understand.

02:35.520 --> 02:37.079
Why must you make me marry Yan Xun?

02:37.079 --> 02:38.190
Don't you like him?

02:38.190 --> 02:39.450
Why are you doing this?

02:40.710 --> 02:42.840
Do you think I still care about Yan Xun?

02:44.430 --> 02:46.360
Have you forgotten what I told you?

02:46.960 --> 02:48.690
I just want you to be miserable.

02:49.000 --> 02:50.560
I want you to watch the people around you

02:50.560 --> 02:52.180
get implicated because of you

02:52.180 --> 02:53.420
and suffer.

02:54.240 --> 02:55.280
Open the door!

02:57.900 --> 02:59.740
Because you're a jinx,

03:00.430 --> 03:01.470
everyone around you

03:01.470 --> 03:03.000
will be dragged down by you.

03:03.240 --> 03:04.590
Are you going to agree or not?

03:04.590 --> 03:06.590
Are you going to open the door or not?

03:37.710 --> 03:38.510
Zhao Chun'er,

03:39.370 --> 03:40.650
you are truly insane.

03:45.750 --> 03:47.320
I am the future Queen of Great Yan!

03:47.320 --> 03:48.720
Who dares to be insolent?

03:50.329 --> 03:50.960
Stop!

04:02.800 --> 04:03.360
Chun'er.

04:04.310 --> 04:05.240
Are you alright?

04:07.240 --> 04:08.100
Your Highness,

04:08.360 --> 04:09.120
you're here.

04:11.310 --> 04:12.040
Princess Fu,

04:12.470 --> 04:13.960
let's leave it here for today.

04:13.960 --> 04:16.019
Don't blow things out of proportion.

04:22.160 --> 04:22.870
Brothers,

04:23.360 --> 04:25.020
I will definitely rescue you.

05:51.550 --> 05:56.720
[REBIRTH]

05:57.250 --> 05:59.650
[Episode 18]

06:08.160 --> 06:08.920
Lady Chu,

06:09.800 --> 06:11.000
can we talk upstairs?

06:11.310 --> 06:13.510
What do you want with me, General Cheng?

06:13.870 --> 06:15.270
Trying to kill me again?

06:19.040 --> 06:20.860
I have no personal grudge against you.

06:20.860 --> 06:21.690
We were on opposite sides before

06:21.690 --> 06:23.510
just because of different positions.

06:23.510 --> 06:25.040
That's not the case anymore.

06:25.040 --> 06:26.280
We now share the same interests,

06:26.280 --> 06:27.750
so we can put aside our differences

06:27.750 --> 06:29.350
and talk about cooperation.

06:39.800 --> 06:41.659
I can help you escape from Yan Xun.

06:41.920 --> 06:43.190
What are you up to?

06:43.510 --> 06:44.870
I don't care about you.

06:46.510 --> 06:48.270
I just don't want to see Yan Xun

06:48.630 --> 06:50.960
become more and more crazy because of you.

06:51.070 --> 06:52.070
What I want

06:52.909 --> 06:55.200
is a wise King of Great Yan.

06:55.830 --> 06:57.360
Why are you telling me this?

06:57.480 --> 07:00.280
Because you are the only one
who can influence him.

07:00.560 --> 07:02.070
If you leave him,

07:03.120 --> 07:05.600
it might make him less arrogant and cruel.

07:05.600 --> 07:08.730
That would be a good thing
for me and the entire Great Yan.

07:09.240 --> 07:10.840
How do you want to cooperate?

07:26.950 --> 07:28.430
You are not fully recovered.

07:28.430 --> 07:30.360
Stay a few more days
and recover before you leave.

07:30.360 --> 07:32.420
You should give me what you promised.

07:55.040 --> 07:57.170
King Ximeng wants me to take your life.

07:57.270 --> 07:58.600
I can't die yet.

07:58.600 --> 07:59.830
If you don't die,

08:00.350 --> 08:01.990
my tribe and I will!

08:25.560 --> 08:26.600
Your poison is acting up.

08:26.600 --> 08:27.730
Rather than suffer,

08:28.150 --> 08:29.750
I might as well end it for you.

08:32.909 --> 08:34.820
Your injuries are not fully recovered yet.

08:34.820 --> 08:36.059
If we fight now,

08:36.200 --> 08:38.000
I won't let you go back alive.

08:38.720 --> 08:39.780
He has no antidote.

08:39.870 --> 08:41.440
He won't last more than a few days.

08:41.440 --> 08:42.970
Stay with him while you can.

08:49.000 --> 08:49.720
Zhuge Yue?

08:50.600 --> 08:51.870
Zhuge Yue! Zhuge Yue!

08:52.710 --> 08:54.280
Zhuge Yue, wake up!

08:55.270 --> 08:56.000
Zhuge Yue...

08:57.310 --> 08:58.080
wake up.

09:03.670 --> 09:04.390
Chun'er!

09:04.910 --> 09:06.310
What exactly do you want?

09:06.720 --> 09:07.790
You've already achieved your goal.

09:07.790 --> 09:09.390
Why did you provoke Chu Qiao?

09:10.550 --> 09:11.240
Chun'er,

09:12.120 --> 09:13.780
you weren't like this before.

09:13.790 --> 09:16.320
Ever since you met Chu Qiao,
you've become...

09:17.670 --> 09:18.480
Go on.

09:19.080 --> 09:20.140
What have I become?

09:20.440 --> 09:21.820
You've become twisted and terrifying,

09:21.820 --> 09:23.620
nothing like the Chun'er I knew.

09:28.720 --> 09:29.320
Li Yan,

09:30.600 --> 09:31.550
you're right.

09:32.110 --> 09:33.570
You are absolutely right.

09:33.630 --> 09:35.080
Every time I see Chu Qiao,

09:36.080 --> 09:38.210
I feel like I'm trapped in a nightmare.

09:38.550 --> 09:39.750
In that nightmare,

09:40.440 --> 09:42.320
I'm a hideous monster!

09:43.720 --> 09:44.850
I'm sorry, Chun'er.

09:45.000 --> 09:46.530
I shouldn't have said that.

09:47.120 --> 09:48.780
You are not a hideous monster.

09:49.000 --> 09:50.930
You're the person I treasure most.

09:53.790 --> 09:54.480
Li Yan,

09:55.200 --> 09:56.460
you don't understand.

09:57.270 --> 09:59.070
You're loving the wrong person.

10:00.150 --> 10:01.720
You never truly knew me.

10:04.390 --> 10:06.000
I've always been ugly

10:06.840 --> 10:07.670
and broken.

10:09.790 --> 10:11.030
The Chun'er you loved

10:12.240 --> 10:14.000
was killed by Yan Xun long ago.

10:16.070 --> 10:17.360
On the day of my wedding,

10:17.360 --> 10:18.790
the moment he rebelled,

10:19.390 --> 10:21.550
he killed me once mercilessly.

10:21.960 --> 10:23.760
In the reed marshes of Great Yan,

10:24.360 --> 10:26.080
those soldiers humiliated me

10:26.600 --> 10:27.660
and trampled on me.

10:28.510 --> 10:30.440
That was when I died all over again.

10:30.930 --> 10:32.560
Chun'er, say no more.

10:34.120 --> 10:36.030
Chu Qiao saw it with her own eyes!

10:36.630 --> 10:38.910
She saw my most humiliating moment.

10:40.120 --> 10:41.550
I hate her so much.

10:41.810 --> 10:42.760
Why?

10:44.030 --> 10:45.960
Why could she, just a slave,

10:46.670 --> 10:48.340
act so high and mighty

10:48.370 --> 10:50.250
while she watched me get pinned down
and humiliated

10:50.250 --> 10:51.580
by those people?

10:52.000 --> 10:53.980
Why was it so easy for a slave like her

10:53.980 --> 10:56.650
to ruin my life?

11:01.550 --> 11:02.120
Li Yan,

11:03.080 --> 11:04.600
you didn't expect this, did you?

11:04.600 --> 11:05.840
The Chun'er you like

11:06.150 --> 11:07.670
is a naked,

11:07.790 --> 11:10.240
filthy monster.

11:12.630 --> 11:13.970
If you regret it now...

11:14.000 --> 11:14.670
Chun'er!

11:16.440 --> 11:17.120
Chun'er!

11:18.360 --> 11:20.360
No matter what you've been through,

11:20.790 --> 11:22.240
I will not leave you.

11:23.630 --> 11:26.030
I am willing to love
every one of your wounds

11:26.550 --> 11:28.480
and endure the suffering with you.

11:35.080 --> 11:37.030
Will you really not despise me?

11:37.270 --> 11:37.910
Chun'er,

11:38.840 --> 11:40.900
no matter what kind of person you are,

11:41.080 --> 11:42.540
I will always stay with you

11:42.910 --> 11:44.170
for the rest of my life.

11:45.000 --> 11:46.660
For all those who wronged you,

11:47.790 --> 11:50.480
I will make them pay double for you.

12:02.670 --> 12:04.930
[Qifeng Palace]

12:27.240 --> 12:28.150
Your Majesty.

12:29.120 --> 12:30.440
I'll marry Yan Xun.

12:31.000 --> 12:32.670
I knew you would come.

12:37.120 --> 12:39.360
I like making deals with smart people.

12:39.510 --> 12:40.750
Then I still can't

12:40.960 --> 12:42.270
compare to you.

12:42.390 --> 12:44.390
I can marry Yan Xun for Li Ce's sake.

12:44.750 --> 12:45.720
But you

12:45.790 --> 12:47.050
can kill your own child

12:47.080 --> 12:48.910
for the sake of power.

13:00.910 --> 13:02.910
You have so many scars on your hands.

13:03.600 --> 13:04.510
Does it hurt?

13:07.720 --> 13:10.050
Thank you for your concern, Your Majesty.

13:10.630 --> 13:11.840
They are old wounds.

13:12.630 --> 13:13.910
They don't hurt anymore.

13:13.910 --> 13:15.120
A woman's hands

13:15.140 --> 13:16.570
must be beautiful.

13:36.960 --> 13:38.290
What are you afraid of, General Chu?

13:38.290 --> 13:39.750
This White Jade Suet Cream

13:40.840 --> 13:42.550
is made from the fat extracted

13:42.550 --> 13:43.360
from the tenderest part

13:43.360 --> 13:45.420
of newborn lambs in the Snowy Region.

13:46.200 --> 13:48.080
It melts when applied to the hands.

13:48.080 --> 13:51.010
It's the best thing
for moisturizing a woman's skin.

13:51.480 --> 13:53.320
I'm going to tell you a story.

13:54.120 --> 13:55.320
When you finish listening,

13:55.320 --> 13:57.120
your hands will be moisturized.

13:59.950 --> 14:01.640
There once was a woman.

14:01.720 --> 14:04.550
Her husband fought with his brother
over the family inheritance

14:04.550 --> 14:05.910
and was killed.

14:07.270 --> 14:09.270
The woman was pregnant.

14:09.600 --> 14:12.080
To save her and her unborn child,

14:14.560 --> 14:17.390
-she begged her brother-in-law for mercy.
-Your Highness!

14:17.390 --> 14:19.080
I am willing to give up any status

14:19.080 --> 14:20.600
to serve by your side.

14:20.720 --> 14:22.320
She even gave herself to him,

14:22.320 --> 14:23.850
hoping to use her sincerity

14:23.870 --> 14:26.200
in exchange for her and her child's lives.

14:26.670 --> 14:28.270
The man agreed.

14:28.440 --> 14:29.870
He took her body

14:30.480 --> 14:32.240
and claimed that

14:32.550 --> 14:34.210
he had fallen in love with her.

14:34.390 --> 14:35.620
But secretly,

14:35.870 --> 14:37.750
he still had her child killed.

14:38.370 --> 14:41.440
From now on, you are my beloved concubine.

14:41.910 --> 14:43.390
I will certainly keep

14:43.550 --> 14:44.510
my promise to you.

14:44.510 --> 14:46.600
I will let his child grow up safely.

14:46.600 --> 14:49.670
The Prince Consort of Chang is about
as far along in her pregnancy as you,

14:49.670 --> 14:50.930
and she is due soon too.

14:51.480 --> 14:52.880
Your Majesty, do you mean

14:53.900 --> 14:55.830
you want to send the child in my womb

14:56.120 --> 14:58.320
to the Prince of Chang's Mansion
to be raised?

14:58.320 --> 14:59.290
If the child is born and lives there

14:59.290 --> 15:01.800
as the son of the Prince of Chang,

15:01.910 --> 15:03.070
when he grows up,

15:03.360 --> 15:05.030
I will grant him official rank
and noble titles,

15:05.030 --> 15:07.550
and let him enjoy a life
of wealth and honor.

15:08.630 --> 15:09.430
Your Majesty,

15:10.080 --> 15:11.600
His Majesty has ordered me

15:11.890 --> 15:12.690
to take

15:12.720 --> 15:14.660
the little Heir Apparent to the palace

15:14.660 --> 15:17.660
for a routine pulse check
by the imperial physicians.

15:19.360 --> 15:21.090
Just one little Heir Apparent?

15:22.390 --> 15:23.030
Yes.

15:23.510 --> 15:24.720
Just one.

15:26.440 --> 15:27.440
Your Majesty!

15:28.510 --> 15:29.840
Yan Qing, what's wrong?

15:30.440 --> 15:31.840
The little Heir Apparent

15:32.200 --> 15:33.660
contracted the plague...

15:34.030 --> 15:35.320
and has passed away.

15:35.480 --> 15:36.960
The man lied to the woman,

15:37.240 --> 15:39.370
telling her the child died of illness.

15:40.150 --> 15:41.720
The woman knew he was lying,

15:42.030 --> 15:43.420
but to survive,

15:43.440 --> 15:44.940
she couldn't expose him.

15:45.670 --> 15:47.510
She could only smile

15:47.790 --> 15:49.200
and play along with him.

15:49.870 --> 15:50.670
Later,

15:50.750 --> 15:52.480
this woman got pregnant again

15:53.320 --> 15:55.390
and gave birth to the man's child.

15:55.790 --> 15:57.270
Looking at the child,

15:57.510 --> 15:58.840
she was in immense pain,

15:59.200 --> 16:01.720
feeling that she had failed her child
who had died.

16:01.720 --> 16:02.630
Day and night,

16:02.650 --> 16:04.150
she heard the cries

16:04.150 --> 16:05.720
of the dead child.

16:23.030 --> 16:24.750
If you were this woman,

16:25.030 --> 16:26.240
what would you do?

16:26.910 --> 16:27.840
What about Li Ce?

16:29.000 --> 16:30.200
Isn't he innocent?

16:30.720 --> 16:32.200
No matter how much suffering
you've endured,

16:32.200 --> 16:32.720
you shouldn't

16:32.720 --> 16:34.580
make him pay for your grievances.

16:38.030 --> 16:39.120
Then tell me,

16:40.270 --> 16:42.000
aren't the slaves of Qingshan Manor
in Great Yong

16:42.000 --> 16:43.080
innocent?

16:43.790 --> 16:45.790
Aren't the soldiers
on the battlefield of Great Yan

16:45.790 --> 16:46.910
innocent?

16:47.510 --> 16:48.240
Slaves

16:48.320 --> 16:49.630
have the fate of slaves.

16:49.630 --> 16:51.630
Soldiers have the fate of soldiers.

16:52.080 --> 16:53.720
As the crown prince of the royal family,

16:53.720 --> 16:55.360
he also has his fate.

16:56.750 --> 16:58.080
This is his fate,

17:01.630 --> 17:02.870
and it is mine as well.

17:05.000 --> 17:06.440
You simply don't understand

17:06.440 --> 17:07.680
what men are,

17:08.109 --> 17:09.440
or what power is.

17:10.750 --> 17:11.720
Attachments

17:11.880 --> 17:14.609
are meant to hold back fools
who trap themselves.

17:15.480 --> 17:17.069
I became the Empress

17:17.920 --> 17:20.180
not because His Majesty loved me so much,

17:20.200 --> 17:22.530
but because I could do many things
for him,

17:23.069 --> 17:24.680
allowing him to rest easy.

17:25.069 --> 17:26.240
Do you think His Majesty doesn't know

17:26.240 --> 17:29.350
there are many doubts about
the Crown Prince's assassination?

17:29.350 --> 17:31.000
But his fear

17:31.000 --> 17:32.960
is more important than anything else.

17:32.960 --> 17:35.510
He would rather kill his own son
by mistake.

17:39.200 --> 17:40.860
In the face of imperial power,

17:41.400 --> 17:42.310
attachments

17:42.720 --> 17:44.350
are not worth mentioning.

17:45.310 --> 17:47.920
You don't have to hold a grudge
against His Majesty,

17:47.920 --> 17:48.750
because you

17:48.960 --> 17:50.310
are just like him.

17:50.790 --> 17:52.520
You are the same kind of people.

17:55.720 --> 17:56.550
You're wrong.

17:58.310 --> 18:00.350
I have put a great deal of effort

18:00.880 --> 18:02.790
into becoming like them.

18:03.350 --> 18:04.880
The Crown Prince is my son,

18:06.200 --> 18:07.860
but more than that, he is a man.

18:09.000 --> 18:10.750
I may not understand my son,

18:11.920 --> 18:12.960
but in my life,

18:13.030 --> 18:14.400
I have seen too many men,

18:14.830 --> 18:16.360
enough to understand them.

18:17.310 --> 18:18.350
I imitate them,

18:18.960 --> 18:20.220
trying to become them,

18:20.510 --> 18:22.030
so that I can survive

18:22.030 --> 18:23.160
in this palace.

18:24.160 --> 18:25.830
You may like Li Ce now.

18:26.590 --> 18:27.400
But that's only because

18:27.400 --> 18:29.000
he hasn't seized power yet.

18:30.400 --> 18:31.460
He still needs you.

18:32.070 --> 18:33.440
Once he seizes power,

18:33.440 --> 18:35.960
he will become
a completely different person.

18:35.960 --> 18:38.350
Think of Yan Xun, whom you once helped.

18:39.070 --> 18:40.110
I know Li Ce.

18:40.350 --> 18:41.550
He is not Yan Xun.

18:44.550 --> 18:45.480
Miss Chu,

18:46.350 --> 18:47.950
you are indeed interesting.

18:48.830 --> 18:50.510
Unlike most people

18:50.510 --> 18:51.510
in this palace.

18:52.830 --> 18:54.350
I will give you a chance.

18:55.160 --> 18:57.030
If you don't want to marry Yan Xun,

18:57.480 --> 18:59.480
you can choose to stand on my side

18:59.960 --> 19:01.270
and work for me.

19:01.960 --> 19:02.820
What do you say?

19:09.030 --> 19:09.890
I'll marry him.

19:22.770 --> 19:24.030
But I have one request.

19:25.750 --> 19:26.950
Before I get married,

19:28.160 --> 19:29.890
I want to see Li Ce one last time.

19:42.350 --> 19:44.070
I've told you so many times.

19:44.070 --> 19:45.310
Don't bother me.

19:51.270 --> 19:51.960
Fu?

19:52.920 --> 19:54.120
You're here to see me?

19:55.070 --> 19:55.720
Li Ce,

19:57.200 --> 19:58.200
you've suffered.

20:02.680 --> 20:04.010
What are you doing here?

20:04.030 --> 20:05.290
I don't want to see you.

20:05.440 --> 20:06.770
You don't want to see me?

20:07.720 --> 20:10.310
Then who was smiling so happily just now?

20:10.440 --> 20:11.350
Who was happy?

20:13.400 --> 20:14.790
Don't flatter yourself.

20:14.790 --> 20:16.070
I brought you back to Biantang

20:16.070 --> 20:17.830
hoping you could help me.

20:18.310 --> 20:19.240
Now look what has happened.

20:19.240 --> 20:20.100
Because of you,

20:20.240 --> 20:21.160
not only have I been accused

20:21.160 --> 20:22.620
of colluding with Ximeng,

20:22.830 --> 20:24.960
but I've also lost my position
as Crown Prince.

20:24.960 --> 20:26.290
What are you doing here?

20:27.440 --> 20:29.880
Get as far away from me as possible.

20:31.240 --> 20:33.040
Don't come to bother me anymore.

20:43.070 --> 20:43.680
Li Ce,

20:44.270 --> 20:46.000
I'm marrying Yan Xun tomorrow.

20:46.920 --> 20:47.850
What did you say?

20:48.110 --> 20:49.640
I am going to Great Yan soon.

20:50.480 --> 20:51.540
Is that far enough?

20:53.590 --> 20:54.240
Qiao.

20:55.110 --> 20:56.070
What's going on?

20:58.830 --> 20:59.960
If I marry Yan Xun,

21:01.480 --> 21:03.480
the Empress will let you leave here,

21:03.830 --> 21:05.510
and you will be able to save your life.

21:05.510 --> 21:07.400
You may no longer be the Crown Prince,

21:07.400 --> 21:09.160
but I didn't touch the money

21:09.790 --> 21:10.990
you left in that shop.

21:11.310 --> 21:12.640
It should be enough
for the rest of your life.

21:12.640 --> 21:14.000
Qiao, are you crazy?

21:15.000 --> 21:16.030
You nearly died

21:16.030 --> 21:16.880
escaping from Great Yan,

21:16.880 --> 21:18.110
and now you want to go back?

21:18.110 --> 21:19.830
I told you I was just using you.

21:19.830 --> 21:22.110
You don't need to get involved
in my affairs at all.

21:22.110 --> 21:23.510
I left that money for you.

21:24.270 --> 21:25.590
Take the money and leave right away.

21:25.590 --> 21:26.350
Go!

21:27.270 --> 21:27.920
Li Ce,

21:29.480 --> 21:30.740
I am the all-powerful,

21:31.170 --> 21:32.820
invincible General Chu.

21:34.000 --> 21:34.880
Trust me.

21:35.070 --> 21:36.550
I will get you out of here.

22:04.030 --> 22:06.160
Isn't this Zhuge Yue's shadow puppet?

22:27.110 --> 22:27.910
Your Majesty,

22:28.480 --> 22:30.540
we are ordered by the King of Great Yan

22:30.550 --> 22:32.350
to prepare your wedding makeup.

22:32.510 --> 22:33.920
It's not my first time.

22:38.550 --> 22:41.680
I am very familiar
with the wedding customs of Great Yan.

22:42.310 --> 22:43.720
I know what to do.

22:46.180 --> 22:47.570
[Boque Palace]

23:06.400 --> 23:07.260
Your Highness!

23:09.160 --> 23:09.790
Lin Mu?

23:14.920 --> 23:15.510
Open it!

23:16.720 --> 23:17.580
Your Highness!

23:19.720 --> 23:20.310
Yan Xun.

23:20.880 --> 23:22.160
The Empress promised me

23:22.160 --> 23:23.350
that as long as I agreed
to the marriage alliance,

23:23.350 --> 23:24.920
my companions would be released.

23:24.920 --> 23:26.650
You are going back on your word!

23:26.680 --> 23:27.350
Chu,

23:28.480 --> 23:29.880
this is the dowry

23:30.550 --> 23:33.000
I requested
from the Empress for Princess Fu.

23:33.000 --> 23:35.600
It's a long journey
from Biantang to Great Yan.

23:36.640 --> 23:38.270
In order to prevent unexpected events,

23:38.270 --> 23:40.930
I have to prepare something in advance,
don't I?

23:43.160 --> 23:43.890
Don't worry.

23:44.480 --> 23:45.710
Provisions in Great Yan are precious.

23:45.710 --> 23:46.880
We don't feed idlers.

23:46.880 --> 23:49.650
As long as Princess Fu arrives safely
in Great Yan,

23:49.650 --> 23:51.510
I will release them immediately.

23:55.640 --> 23:57.590
According to Her Majesty's decree,

23:57.590 --> 23:59.790
Crown Prince Li Ce has been disrespectful.

23:59.790 --> 24:02.030
He is stripped of his title
as Crown Prince

24:02.030 --> 24:03.440
and demoted to a commoner.

24:03.440 --> 24:05.830
He is exiled to his fief in Youzhou
and confined there.

24:05.830 --> 24:07.510
He shall depart today.

24:09.160 --> 24:09.750
I...

24:11.440 --> 24:12.570
receive the decree.

24:20.880 --> 24:21.590
Li Ce,

24:22.270 --> 24:23.070
trust me.

24:23.350 --> 24:25.410
I will definitely get you out of here.

24:27.550 --> 24:28.410
Your Highness,

24:29.020 --> 24:31.400
you've been staring at this shadow puppet
all the way.

24:31.400 --> 24:33.240
Does it have some special meaning?

24:33.240 --> 24:33.800
Shut up.

24:46.000 --> 24:48.680
This shadow puppet is a secret signal
from Qiao.

24:49.350 --> 24:50.680
It can help us escape.

24:50.960 --> 24:52.160
It's very important.

25:03.790 --> 25:05.450
Gentlemen, your tea is ready.

25:36.960 --> 25:37.550
S-Sir.

25:37.550 --> 25:38.550
Your cup is full.

25:40.110 --> 25:40.830
Thank you.

25:40.890 --> 25:41.750
Enjoy your tea.

25:52.070 --> 25:52.930
Your Highness.

26:10.430 --> 26:11.500
Coming.

26:13.640 --> 26:14.300
Here you go.

26:15.640 --> 26:16.400
Enjoy.

26:16.960 --> 26:17.550
Sir.

26:22.240 --> 26:23.920
It's him! It's him!

26:26.550 --> 26:28.650
This shadow puppet is beautifully made.

26:28.650 --> 26:29.510
Enjoy your tea.

26:33.310 --> 26:34.170
Your Highness,

26:34.270 --> 26:35.800
it seems this shadow puppet

26:35.880 --> 26:37.540
doesn't have any special use.

26:39.160 --> 26:39.890
Don't worry.

26:40.440 --> 26:41.720
Qiao will definitely find a way

26:41.720 --> 26:42.510
to save us.

27:10.330 --> 27:11.190
Your Highness.

27:11.550 --> 27:12.000
Your Highness.

27:12.000 --> 27:13.110
Qiao is here to save us?

27:13.110 --> 27:13.680
No.

27:14.660 --> 27:16.990
This doesn't seem to be the official road.

27:28.240 --> 27:29.270
Why did we stop?

27:30.720 --> 27:32.980
Don't panic. I'll go down and take a look.

27:37.750 --> 27:39.030
Where are they?

27:51.590 --> 27:52.650
Where is everyone?

27:58.480 --> 27:59.400
Great!

28:00.160 --> 28:01.360
You're finally here!

28:01.480 --> 28:02.480
What did I say?

28:02.720 --> 28:05.380
I told you Qiao would definitely
come to save us.

28:05.830 --> 28:08.560
I'm afraid I will disappoint you,
Your Highness.

28:10.590 --> 28:12.650
Her Majesty specifically ordered me

28:13.130 --> 28:15.650
to send you to hell.

28:16.720 --> 28:17.310
No.

28:17.830 --> 28:19.830
You have been demoted to a commoner.

28:20.030 --> 28:22.020
You don't deserve
to be called Your Highness anymore.

28:22.020 --> 28:23.200
Zhan Ziyu!

28:24.430 --> 28:26.170
Don't think you can do whatever you want

28:26.170 --> 28:27.790
just because Her Majesty
is backing you up.

28:27.790 --> 28:29.510
The people coming to save me
will be here soon.

28:29.510 --> 28:31.920
I knew someone would come to save you,

28:32.240 --> 28:34.570
so I specifically chose this road for you.

28:34.590 --> 28:36.110
By the time your people arrive,

28:36.110 --> 28:38.440
they can only collect your corpse.

28:41.480 --> 28:43.210
I am no longer the Crown Prince.

28:43.640 --> 28:45.770
I will no longer pose any threat to her.

28:46.270 --> 28:47.130
I didn't expect

28:47.550 --> 28:49.270
she still wouldn't let me go.

28:49.510 --> 28:50.270
What a pity.

28:50.720 --> 28:52.240
Although you are her son,

28:52.350 --> 28:54.510
you don't know her at all.

28:54.510 --> 28:55.350
You're wrong!

28:56.350 --> 28:57.540
I know her too well!

28:58.420 --> 28:59.860
I just thought that

29:01.510 --> 29:03.970
no matter what conflict I had
with my mother,

29:04.400 --> 29:06.160
we were still blood,

29:07.270 --> 29:09.030
and things would never come to this.

29:09.030 --> 29:10.860
You think that to Her Majesty,

29:10.890 --> 29:13.170
you're only a threat to her power?

29:13.510 --> 29:15.030
Your very existence

29:15.030 --> 29:16.360
is a humiliation to her.

29:16.920 --> 29:18.920
Only when you completely disappear

29:19.350 --> 29:21.000
can she truly feel at ease.

30:00.920 --> 30:02.520
Let's see how far you can run.

30:12.110 --> 30:12.870
Song Cheng!

30:12.920 --> 30:14.050
Run, Your Highness!

30:19.640 --> 30:20.510
Run!

30:56.550 --> 30:57.200
Take him.

31:04.480 --> 31:05.090
Minglu.

31:08.030 --> 31:08.680
Minglu?

31:09.240 --> 31:10.000
You actually...

31:10.000 --> 31:11.000
Cut the crap!

31:11.780 --> 31:12.350
Minglu,

31:12.510 --> 31:13.710
take them and go first.

31:13.710 --> 31:15.310
I still have something to do.

31:29.200 --> 31:30.330
Assemble the troops

31:30.450 --> 31:31.710
and prepare to depart!

31:36.350 --> 31:37.880
Consort Helian is missing.

31:39.830 --> 31:40.590
What is it?

31:43.000 --> 31:43.800
Your Majesty,

31:44.110 --> 31:45.640
Consort Helian is missing.

31:46.180 --> 31:46.900
Missing?

31:47.240 --> 31:48.040
Your Majesty,

31:48.750 --> 31:49.750
Consort Helian

31:49.750 --> 31:51.440
said she was going for a walk nearby

31:51.440 --> 31:52.900
and went to that hillside.

31:53.110 --> 31:54.550
But when the maids went to look for her,

31:54.550 --> 31:55.680
she was not there.

31:56.030 --> 31:56.680
We've already sent people

31:56.680 --> 31:58.270
to search the entire hillside,

31:58.270 --> 31:59.600
but they found nothing.

31:59.920 --> 32:00.980
Then keep looking.

32:01.400 --> 32:03.750
Where could she possibly go alone?

32:04.000 --> 32:04.550
Yes.

32:06.030 --> 32:07.200
You guys, follow me!

32:16.310 --> 32:17.480
Split up and search!

32:25.920 --> 32:26.680
Go now.

32:27.030 --> 32:29.310
Yan Xun should only be delayed
for a short while.

32:29.310 --> 32:30.880
I can't go alone.

32:31.060 --> 32:33.790
I have to take everyone
in the prison cart with me.

32:34.030 --> 32:34.760
Impossible.

32:35.480 --> 32:36.940
I only agreed to let you go.

32:37.200 --> 32:39.200
Those people aren't part of our deal.

32:39.200 --> 32:40.030
Well now,

32:41.680 --> 32:42.880
the deal has changed.

32:53.440 --> 32:54.900
Though I'm from Great Yan,

32:55.160 --> 32:56.760
I've heard that in Biantang,

32:57.160 --> 33:00.020
the god here governs
the love between men and women.

33:00.200 --> 33:03.310
I pray that you bless His Majesty
so he may achieve his heart's desire

33:03.310 --> 33:05.840
and be happily united
with Queen Chu forever.

33:06.160 --> 33:08.030
I am willing to spend my life
in vegetarian devotion and accumulate merit,

33:08.030 --> 33:12.360
only in exchange for His Majesty
and his beloved being together in happiness.

33:15.750 --> 33:17.810
How could you believe in such a thing?

33:18.000 --> 33:18.800
Your Majesty?

33:19.240 --> 33:20.240
Utterly foolish.

33:21.510 --> 33:22.440
I am ignorant.

33:23.030 --> 33:26.350
I saw Your Majesty
worrying because of Queen Chu

33:26.790 --> 33:29.030
but didn't know how to ease your burden.

33:29.350 --> 33:30.880
I just heard from the mountain people
on the road

33:30.880 --> 33:32.200
that this temple is very efficacious,

33:32.200 --> 33:33.880
so I wanted to come up
and pay my respects.

33:33.880 --> 33:35.480
Everyone is waiting for you.

33:36.030 --> 33:37.110
Don't waste time.

34:14.560 --> 34:15.760
Run! Run!

34:15.780 --> 34:16.739
Hurry! Hurry!

34:17.030 --> 34:17.670
Let's go!

34:33.880 --> 34:34.630
Your Majesty,

34:34.630 --> 34:36.590
while we were looking for Consort Helian,

34:36.590 --> 34:37.480
Chu Qiao escaped in the chaos.

34:37.480 --> 34:38.630
It is my fault.

34:39.030 --> 34:40.830
Please punish me, Your Majesty.

35:04.480 --> 35:05.280
Your Majesty,

35:05.280 --> 35:06.480
it's all my fault.

35:06.710 --> 35:08.510
If Your Majesty
hadn't been looking for me,

35:08.510 --> 35:09.150
Her Majesty wouldn't have...

35:09.150 --> 35:10.750
Get in the wedding carriage.

35:11.950 --> 35:12.750
Your Majesty?

35:17.150 --> 35:19.550
I told you to get into
the wedding carriage.

35:51.670 --> 35:52.470
Your Majesty.

35:52.760 --> 35:54.030
Now that Chu Qiao has run away,

35:54.030 --> 35:55.630
she will definitely return to Tangjing.

35:55.630 --> 35:57.630
Should we inform Biantang Empress?

35:59.760 --> 36:00.400
Let's go.

36:01.610 --> 36:03.540
Return to the Capital of Great Yan.

36:12.280 --> 36:14.540
Didn't we agree to meet at the residence?

36:14.980 --> 36:15.910
Why are you here?

36:16.150 --> 36:18.070
I was afraid you'd change your mind

36:18.070 --> 36:20.070
and go back to Great Yan with Yan Xun.

36:20.880 --> 36:21.800
I didn't know

36:22.280 --> 36:24.280
that Lord Zhuge could get angry too.

36:24.960 --> 36:25.920
Couldn't you tell

36:25.920 --> 36:27.190
I've been angry all these days?

36:27.190 --> 36:28.450
I really couldn't.

36:29.530 --> 36:31.260
Whether you're angry or not,

36:31.510 --> 36:33.230
you always have a frozen face.

36:46.320 --> 36:47.070
Chu,

36:47.910 --> 36:49.710
I prepared this for you.

37:04.510 --> 37:05.400
Do you like it?

37:19.510 --> 37:20.150
Chu,

37:21.880 --> 37:23.740
let me draw your eyebrows for you.

37:27.800 --> 37:28.710
Do you remember

37:29.510 --> 37:31.370
when we were in Yingge Courtyard,

37:31.510 --> 37:33.370
I also drew your eyebrows for you?

37:37.190 --> 37:39.590
You promised to go back to Great Yan
with me.

37:40.670 --> 37:41.880
But why?

37:42.480 --> 37:44.540
Why would you rather stay in Biantang

37:45.320 --> 37:47.550
with that incompetent Crown Prince

37:48.550 --> 37:50.360
than go back with me?

37:54.670 --> 37:55.470
Your Majesty.

37:56.920 --> 37:57.920
Look at me.

38:02.150 --> 38:03.800
I am not Queen Chu.

38:09.880 --> 38:11.610
Didn't you want to be Queen Chu?

38:12.190 --> 38:14.590
Haven't you always wanted to replace her?

38:15.510 --> 38:17.000
I'm giving you the chance.

38:19.400 --> 38:20.920
Why aren't you taking it?

38:40.590 --> 38:42.450
I thought you were a smart person.

38:43.190 --> 38:45.550
I didn't expect you to be so stupid too.

38:45.550 --> 38:46.360
Princess Fu!

38:46.360 --> 38:49.670
Do you know that
holding the Empress hostage is treason?

38:50.670 --> 38:52.480
You, a deposed Princess,

38:52.510 --> 38:54.590
and me, a useless prince,

38:54.740 --> 38:56.570
are a match made in heaven.

38:56.880 --> 38:57.880
You bold traitor!

38:58.170 --> 38:59.500
To frame me,

38:59.590 --> 39:01.440
you dare to hold His Majesty hostage?
